data.description: Beautiful condo features 2 stories of living space. Entry level includes living room, and eat-in kitchen with exit to the fenced in patio out back. The upper level features 2 bedrooms and a full bath. Main bedroom has private entry to the bathroom. Lower level includes half bath, laundry room and full finished basement. HOA includes clubhouse, gym, and pool. Snow removal and lawn services included.
